data.description: Affordable home in the Lake Limerick community! This is a great opportunity to own with access to fabulous amenities! Golfing, boating, swimming and more! This modest charmer features 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, primary bedroom with walk in closet, utility room, kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, fresh interior paint, new interior doors and a large deck. The .23 acre lot offers plenty of outdoor space. Come take a look at this sweet home and make it your own!
